{"tid":283194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬惜珍唔係死左啦咩？ 乜誹謗係涵蓋到死左既人架咩？","createTime":"2017-06-14T03:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T04:04:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"317b2c7ce11e5a2ce7cac3ae80effb348c6defc0","tid":283194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"乜唔係在生既人既名聲, 先可以係法律上告人誹謗?<br />\n<br />\n死左既人, 告乜柒誹謗?"},{"pid":"02f11e854c1fab325d63bd8c65a2a23e6852a601","tid":283194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://blogs.lexisnexis.co.uk/wipit/can-you-defame-the-dead/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblogs.lexisnexis.co.uk%2Fwipit%2Fcan-you-defame-the-dead%2F&d=ZtF%2B5Weu0h1QVM77lB%2BB2sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b73cd822\" target=\"_blank\">http://blogs.lexisnexis.co.uk/wipit/can-you-defame-the-dead/</a><br />\n<br />\nThe European Court of Human Rights (ECtHR) has rejected a complaint by one of Joseph Stalin&rsquo;s grandsons about an article that appeared in a Russian newspaper in which the dictator was accused of being a &lsquo;bloodthirsty cannibal&rsquo;. Jill Bainbridge, partner and expert in defamation and reputation management at Blake Morgan, explains why the dead cannot be defamed.<br />\nFor the full judgment see: Yevgeniy Yakovlevich Dzhugashvili v Russia (App No 41123/10).<br />\n<br />\nIn short, no. The dead cannot currently be defamed under English law. This is because defamation, whether it is libel or slander, is a personal action which cannot be assigned or brought on someone&rsquo;s behalf."},{"pid":"a23bbff0fffe87a9bac271006869b71091153d93","tid":283194,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27e4fb2e318ebc7cfa5d5cb08fe598e1401d1079","tid":283194,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9be9abcf6011ba69e5bd32d36b48a64203fb77a2","tid":283194,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce0cc02869c7df1f44295af5f91bb9f3f8cae1e5","tid":283194,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"895fe1ee6b06ab4598bedf4e9b6a85d452a45da7","tid":283194,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd03a96ecf5d8189d11adaf551ad6c3cff743cc9","tid":283194,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:43:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64f6da2e5bb3fead163626909c57e056d3d5cc4f","tid":283194,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:04:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}